726809f-a.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 77th Avenue
726809f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway, south from near 77th Avenue,
across the lIndependent System Subway yards. This area
shows the extensive highway junctions of Grand Central
Parkway, Union Turnpike and the Interboro Parkway.
Views 1,2: May 30, 1939
View 3: June 29, 1936
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
